To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private SpinningTop _spinningtop;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_spinningtop = SpinningTop(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_spinningtop.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "period", _spinningtop.Period);
    Plot("My Indicators", "spinningtop", _spinningtop.Current);
}
